'''Bombei Afahyɛ''' (Bayerɛ Afahyɛ) yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Ekyem Kofi a ɛbɛn Sekondi a ɛwɔ Atɔe Mantam wɔ Ghana no di. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so nsɔn no mu<ref>https://touringghana.com/festivals/</ref>.<ref name="ghanaconsulatedubai.com">https://www.ghanaconsulatedubai.com/tourism.html</ref><ref>http://ghanareview.com/festivals2.html</ref><ref>https://tourghana.com/ghana-festivals/</ref><ref>https://www.slutchtours.com/?page_id=21</ref>

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammere ntade ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
